---
import { SITE } from '~/config.mjs';
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

import Hero from '~/components/widgets/Hero.astro';
// import Note from '~/components/widgets/Note.astro';
// import Features from '~/components/widgets/Features.astro';
import Features2 from '~/components/widgets/Features2.astro';
// import Steps from '~/components/widgets/Steps.astro';
import Content from '~/components/widgets/Content.astro';
import LatestPosts from '~/components/blog/LatestPosts.astro';
// import Contactform from '~/components/contactform.astro';

const meta = {
  title: SITE.title,
  description: SITE.description,
  dontUseTitleTemplate: true,
};
---

<Layout {meta}>
  <!-- Hero Widget ******************* -->

  <Hero
    callToAction={{ text: 'Projects', href: '#projects', icon: 'tabler:arrow-down' }}
    image={{ src: import('~/assets/images/ak-banner.png'), alt: 'AstroWind Hero Image' }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="title">
      Empowering women <br />in tech 🚀 <br />
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      <span class="mb-1 font-bold text-primary dark:text-secondary">Aga Kadela</span> - a programmer, entrepreneur, and dedicated
      educator with a passionate mission: empowering women in tech. As the visionary behind Coder Woman School and dotty.ai,
      I'm committed to unleashing the full potential of women as coding superheroes."
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <Content
    id="projects"
    highlight="Projects"
    title="What am I currently working on?"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Learn and grow with Coder Woman School',
      },
      {
        title: 'Meet other coders in Coder Woman Community',
      },
      {
        title: 'Become a coding superhero with us',
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: import('~/assets/images/cw-project.png'),
      alt: 'Coder Woman project screenshot',
    }}
    button={{
      href: 'https://coderwoman.com',
      text: 'See live',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-2">Coder Woman School & Community</h3>
      Ever dreamed of diving into the world of coding but felt a bit lost on where to start? That’s exactly why we created Coder Woman School and Community – your new go-to spot to kickstart your coding journey in the most fun and friendly way possible!

      Here’s the scoop:
      
      Learn Coding from Scratch: We’ve got super easy-to-follow courses on HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It’s like learning a new language, but way cooler and with endless cups of virtual tea! 🍵💻
      Build Your Own Projects: By the end of our courses, you’ll not just learn; you’ll DO! You’ll have your very own projects to show off to the world (or just your friends and family to start with).
      Join a Fab Community: Imagine a place where everyone is rooting for you, sharing tips, and just a message away when you’re stuck. That’s our community! 🌈
      Why join us?
      
      It’s Super Welcoming: No tech background? No problem! We’re all about starting from wherever you are.
      Make Friends Along the Way: Meet awesome women just like you who are starting their tech journey. Coding is more fun together!
      Empower Yourself: There’s something magical about typing a bit of code and creating something amazing. We want you to experience that magic.
      So, are you ready to take the leap and start your coding adventure with a bunch of friends cheering you on? Come join Coder Woman School and Community. Let’s make coding your superpower together! 💪👩‍💻
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

  <Content
    isReversed
    isAfterContent
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Less search, more fun',
      },
      {
        title: "We don't just want you to read - we want you to grow!",
      },
      {
        title: 'For Women, By Women, In Tech',
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: import('~/assets/images/dotty-project.png'),
      alt: 'Dotty project screenshot',
    }}
    button={{
      href: 'https://dotty.ai',
      text: 'See live',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-2">
        Dotty.ai - Where Tech Girls Connect the Dots!
      </h3>
      🌟 Meet Dotty! Where tech girls connect the dots! 🚀

      Ever felt lost in the tech world? 🤷‍♀️ Wondered where to start or what to learn next? Say hello to Dotty! 🎉
      
      Dotty is like a magic map for your tech journey. 🗺️ It listens to what you love, where you're headed, and poof! ✨ Gives you a learning path that feels just right. Whether you're into making websites, diving into data, or anything in between, Dotty's got your back. 🙌
      
      Why Dotty? Because...
      
      It's all about YOU! Your choices, your pace, your adventure. 🌱
      It makes learning fun and not a snooze fest. 😄
      It's easy-peasy to start, and you're never walking alone. 👭
      Ready to turn your tech dreams into reality? Let Dotty guide the way! 🌟 Start your journey today!
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

  <Features2 title="My favorite technologies" subtitle="" highlight="Tools" />

  <LatestPosts
    title="Check out my articles"
    postIds={['rendering-leaflet-clusters-fast-and-dynamically-lets-compare-3-methods.md']}
  />
</Layout>
